<!DOCTYPE html>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="top.css">

  <div class="box">

    <div class="box1">
      <div class="row justify-content-md-center">
        <h2>地名タグ選択</h2>
      </div>
    </div>


    <div class="row justify-content-md-center">
      <p>地名をチェック☑すると、その地名の投稿一覧を閲覧できます。</p>
    </div>

    <div class="container">
      <div class="box2">
        <%= form_tag({controller:"posts",action:"index"}, method: :get) do %>
          <% Tag.all.each do |t| %>
          <div class='form-check d-inline'>
            <%= check_box :tag_ids, t.name %>
            <label for="tag_ids_<%= t.name %>"><%= t.name %></label>
          </div>
          <% end %>
            <%= submit_tag '検索' %>

        <% end %>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>

<style>
  label {
    margin: 0;
    display: inherit;
  }
</style>